Privacy Policy
1. Introduction
Welcome to the "National Weather" or "Calendar Holiday" application (hereinafter referred to as "the App"). We are committed to protecting your privacy. This privacy policy aims to explain how we collect, use, share, and protect your personal information. Please read this privacy policy carefully before using the App.
2. Information We Collect
We may collect the following types of information:
Personal Information
: Such as name, email address, phone number, etc., typically provided when you register an account or contact us.
Usage Data
: Information about your use of the App, including device information, operating system version, IP address, access times, pages viewed, etc.
Location Data
: If you allow, we may collect information about your location to provide accurate weather information.
Other Information
: Any additional information you may voluntarily provide, such as feedback, survey responses, etc.
3. Use of Information
We use the collected information to:
Provide and maintain the functionality and services of the App, including accurate weather forecasts.
Improve the performance and user experience of the App.
Handle user requests and support, including personalized weather notifications.
Send you notifications, updates, and marketing information related to the App (if you agree to receive them).
4. Sharing of Information
We may share your information in the following circumstances:
With Service Providers
: We may share information with third-party service providers to help us provide, maintain, and improve the functionality of the App.
Legal Requirements
: We may disclose your information to comply with legal requirements or protect our rights if required by law.
Business Transfers
: In the event of business reorganization, merger, or sale, your information may be transferred to a new company.
5. Protection of Information
We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is completely secure.
6. Your Rights
Under applicable laws, you may have the following rights:
Right of Access
: You can request access to the personal information we hold about you.
Right to Rectification
: You can request to correct or update inaccurate or incomplete personal information.
Right to Deletion
: You can request to delete your personal information.
Right to Restrict Processing
: You can request to restrict our processing of your personal information.
Right to Object
: You can object to our processing of your personal information based on legitimate interests.
7. Children's Privacy
The App is not intended for children under the age of 13. If we learn that a child under 13 has provided personal information, we will promptly delete such information.
8. Changes to the Privacy Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will post the updated privacy policy on this page and notify you if appropriate. Please check this privacy policy periodically for any changes.
9. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at:
